data = [[23, 24, 25, 27, 26], [0, -1, 1, -3, -2], [9, 10, 11, 12, 11]]

def get_a_days_weather(wdata, day):
  new_list = []
  for i in range(0, len(data)):
    if day >= 0 and day < 5:
      new_list.append(data[0][day])
      new_list.append(data[1][day])
      new_list.append(data[2][day])
      return new_list
    else:
      return "day " + str(day) + " is invalid!"

print(get_a_days_weather(data, 0))
print(get_a_days_weather(data, 2))
print(get_a_days_weather(data, 4))
print(get_a_days_weather(data, 5))
print(get_a_days_weather(data, -1))

data = [[23, 24, 25, 27, 26], [0, -1, 1, -3, -2], [9, 10, 11, 12, 11]]

def get_a_days_weather(wdata, day):
  new_list = []
  for i in range(0, len(data)+2):
    if i == day:
      new_list.append(data[0][i])
      new_list.append(data[1][i])
      new_list.append(data[2][i])
      return new_list
  else:
    return "day " + str(day) + " is invalid"

print(get_a_days_weather(data, 0))
print(get_a_days_weather(data, 2))
print(get_a_days_weather(data, 4))
print(get_a_days_weather(data, 5))
print(get_a_days_weather(data, -1))
